  The WSFS Constitution is also available online
  <%= link_to("here", "http://www.wsfs.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/WSFS-Constitution-as-of-August-19-2019.pdf") %>.
</p>

<p>
  We look forward to your participation in the 2020 Hugo Awards and 1945 Retro
  Hugos, and hope to see you at CoNZealand!
</p>

